"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, this is Scotty here. We're on our regenerative agriculture project. This is Riley the farmer sneezing while he puts on the plenum level. It's a little bit dusty, so that'll happen. And this is just going to cover the irrigation pipe that's going in there so that it diffuses the air a little bit better and so that the compost doesn't compact and uh group around the holes. That will uh get a little bit easier airflow going. And next lever, next uh thing we're doing is we're going to take this pile with the help of a tractor and pile it on this plenum level so uh that the pipe that's blowing air into it through this fan can start aerating it because the limiting factor in compost is oftentimes air. That's what it runs out of very quickly. So once you get the nitrogen right and the carbon right and the water right, it's just air that needs to get put in there regularly, and this is an easy way of doing that. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, this is Scotty here.\",\n      \"start\": 0.64,\n      \"end\": 2.8,\n      \"duration\": 2.16,\n      \"confidence\": 0.989,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.64,\n          \"end\": 0.96,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 0.993\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.96,\n          \"end\": 1.12,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 1.2,\n          \"end\": 1.36,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 1.36,\n          \"end\": 1.52,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 1.52,\n          \"end\": 1.68,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confi